description: This guy seems to have nothing to say for himself.

content.text: First thing first though, dear; you need a ^orange;ship in good working order^reset;. Who knows how far you'll have to travel before we're done. I think you should ^green;return to the Outpost and speak to ^orange;Penguin Pete the shipyard captain^reset;.
content.title: Become Space-worthy
content.completionText: That was no mean feat - well done, dear. Now that your ship is in full working order we can get started on the task at hand.

content.text: I can repair that ship, but it's gonna take 20 ^orange;Erchius Crystals^reset;... You'd better ^green;get yerself over to the Erchius Mining Facility^reset;. I've sent the location coordinates to ^green;yer ship's SAIL^reset;.
content.title: The Erchius Mining Facility
content.completionText: Perfect! These'll do the job. I'll go ahead and fix up yer ship right now.

content.text: Hey there, friendo! I'm ^orange;Dr. Akaggy^white;, and I deal in robots! So I have this experimental ^green;modular space mech^white; in need of a test drive and my usual pilots are... Indisposed. Could you do me a favor and ^green;fly it through my test course^white;?Just ^green;talk to me when you're ready to go^white;!
content.title: ^orange;Test Drive
content.completionText: You made it back! That's not surprise in my voice, it's elation! As a reward, I can give you enough ^green;spare mech components^white; for you to deploy your own mech for space travel! Head over to that ^orange;mech assembly station^white; to customise it!

content.text: I've been developing technology that will enable the user to swiftly dash from one point to another, but I'm lacking a few crucial components for my ^orange;prototype^white;. Could you help me by ^green;bringing me ^orange;10 Copper Bars^white;?
content.title: ^orange;Let's Get Technical
content.completionText: You brought me the parts! Wonderful! With these the ^orange;Dash Tech^white; should be ready for action, but there's only one way to be sure...

content.text: We are currently in orbit around an unknown world. The ship is heavily damaged and we are unable to leave orbit. I suggest you ^green;beam down to the planet's surface using the ^orange;teleporter^white;, and search for supplies and perhaps a means of fixing the ship.
content.title: Getting Started
content.completionText: Thank you for joining me dear. With your help I know we can triumph.

content.text: My ^orange;Dash Tech^white; needs to be properly tested before I can go into mass-production. Would you mind ^green;putting it through its paces on my ^orange;obstacle course^white;? ^green;Talk to me again when you're ready^white; and I can send you there.
content.title: ^orange;A Dashing Individual
content.completionText: The ^orange;Dash Tech^white; appears to be functioning perfectly! Wonderful! Please, keep the Tech as a token of my thanks. I also have other prototypes that need testing, so come and see me again when you're ready.

content.text: I've been working on a new piece of tech that enables the user to perform a jump in mid-air, allowing them to reach incredible new heights! Unfortunately, I require a few more components before I can finish it. ^green;Could you bring me ^orange;10 Silver Bars^white;?
content.title: ^orange;Jump-starting Development
content.completionText: Marvelous! With these additions the ^orange;Pulse Jump Tech^white; is ready for testing! Come and speak to me again if you'd like to help.

content.text: My ^orange;Pulse Jump Tech^white; needs thorough testing before I can begin distributing it. My new ^orange;obstacle course^white; is ready and waiting! ^green;Talk to me again when you decide you're ready to try it out^white;.
content.title: ^orange;Jumping To The Right Conclusion
content.completionText: The ^orange;Pulse Jump Tech^white; appears to be operating wonderfully! Keep that one, you've earned it. ^green;Come see me again when you're ready for more work^white;.

content.text: Greetings! I'm looking for someone to become my ^orange;partner in crime-fighting^white;! If you think you have what it takes, come out into space and meet me at my humble asteroid base!
content.title: Becoming a Peacekeeper
content.completionText: Welcome to your new Peacekeeper Station, partner!

content.text: The ^orange;tech^white; I'm working on now is truly fantastic! It enables the user to compress into a small, spherical form ideal for moving around in tight spaces. I need some final components to finish it. ^green;Could you bring me ^orange;10 Gold Bars^white;?
content.title: ^orange;Rounding Up The Components
content.completionText: Most excellent! Now all that remains is to test the ^orange;Distortion Sphere Tech^white; and I've got just the course for it.

content.text: My ^orange;Distortion Sphere Tech^white; is ready to roll! I'd like you to ^green;test it on the new obstacle course^white; I've set up. You should have no problems getting into any of the narrow spaces inside. ^green;Talk to me again when you're ready to go in.
content.title: ^orange;Getting The Ball Rolling
content.completionText: Excellent! The ^orange;Distortion Sphere Tech^white; performed just as I'd hoped it would. Please, keep it - thanks to you I've been able to make significant strides in my research!

content.text: Help me out, would ya? Business around here hasn't been so great since all my regulars are on the run from ^orange;Dreadwing^white; and his gang of crooks! Can you ^green;go and defeat Dreadwing^white; for me? Come speak when you're ready, I'll send ya right to him!
content.title: ^green;Dreadwing the Penguin
content.completionText: You sorted him out for me? Thanks, now I'm back in business! ^green;Come speak to me if you want a ^orange;Dubloon^green; to hire a penguin merc^white;.

content.text: Now that you're familiar with scanning, ^green;we need to start finding these ^orange;artifacts^white;, dear. Yes, the Floran one first... Their colonies will contain vital ^orange;clues^reset; to its whereabouts. Floran live all over nowadays, but still prefer the dense ^orange;forest^white; vegetation of planets found around ^orange;gentle stars^white;. Good luck dear, and thank you.
content.title: Find Clues to Locate the Floran Artifact
content.completionText: You did it! That was the last clue we needed. I know just where the Floran artifact is now.

content.text: The ship is damaged and you are floating alone in space. Your best bet is to boot up the ship computer and see if anything good comes of it.
content.title: Boot Up
content.completionText: SAIL is awake! Now you have some guidance, and some company.

content.title: The Protectorate
content.completionText: The years of training paid off - you survived graduation day!

content.text: Before you go jetting off, I'll teach you how to ^green;access and use^white; the ^orange;scan mode^white; on your ^orange;Matter Manipulator^white;. There is a lot to be learned from your surroundings, and the Outpost is no exception. ^green;Press ^#71f2f6;[N]^green; to equip your ^orange;scanner^white;, key areas of interest will appear green. Let me know how you get on!
content.title: Visit The Outpost
content.completionText: Excellent work. It may seem trivial, but scanning is an essential skill that will be pivotal in our search for the artifacts.
